latestIgtvVideos.title: SneakPeek Into CC Reserve
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
CC Reserve is now open after putting together 16 years of flirting with coffee ! Now serving specialty coffees with amazing flavour notes of handpicked coffee beans after unlimited trials of 100s of coffee beans from around the world to finally finding the best of the best to be served ! 100% Specialty Grade Arabica coffees - all single estates - with great stories around them to be told. Come - Experience our passion !
So its simple #LetsHaveCoffee & fall in love with it like never before ! 

CC Reserve 
CC Reserve is a commitment to serve the most authentic, high quality & rarest coffee, brewing it to perfection & inspiring to spread coffee culture ! 

Concept : 
Artisanal Coffee Bar (on ground floor)
Single Origin Single Estate Coffees 
- Espresso Bar
- Siphon Bar 
- V60 Bar 
- DIY Bar 
Self Service 
Music : Jazz

Scratch Kitchen (first floor)
- All Day Dining Menu 
- Salads To Desserts 
- Fully Serviced 
- Music : Trending Latest

latestIgtvVideos.title: This Father’s Day..
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Meet the coolest Pop, doin what he does best - (not) make Coldbrews. 
 
Fatherhood brings out the best in you. You know your little babies look upto you and all you wish to be is always a Hero for them. As tiring as it might get at times, it’s the little things our children do that makes it all worth it! 
And while they might take a while to get there - we thought you could use some refreshments! 

Happy Fathers Day ya’ll !
